<br>
In the past week Hayley and Detah have drove away several of the oldest members of FS. Now that Aono is gone Hayley and her puppy dog Detah have pretty much drove it to the point of no return. I am posting this becuase alot of FS will be looking for new homes. Please don't judge them for Hayley and Detahs mistakes 90% of FS are really good players and deserve a fresh start. As for Hayley and Detah stay as far away from them as possible. They are EQ's version of SARS!!!<br>
