<br>
for those that are now wondering why I have deguilded, thats why they make message boards, to explain to the most people the same thing so that there will be no confusion when this is done (yeah right, I'll be all over the place, as usual).. <br>
<br>
bottom line is that I cannot remain an officer of a guild that no longer operates on the best interests of the guild as a whole.. after seein many of my closest friends leave either the guild or this game, I realize that my time playing this game might just be waning as well, and there is no time for the massive pile of negativity thats festered itself within this guild.. I can no longer positively affect any change that might improve the lives of the members of Frozen Spirits, and I realize thats a shocking revelation to hear from an officer.. the only capacity I could fulfill as an officer was to be a positive role model, but those get pretty much ignored in this guild, preferring to emulate the loudest people.. <br>
couple that with being lumped in with the leaders (and raidleader) when so many feel that they are being cheated by those same people, makes me want to distance myself from them as much as possible, becuase this game is all about reputation as a player and as a person, and being lumped in with people that even within the guild have shady reputations, has become too much for me to continue with.. not all of the officers are shady, but the rotten is too close to the core to cut out.. <br>
<br>
Im quite sure I will be blasted for this, and you can go ahead and have at it.. but, I personally have felt for weeks now that the only way this guild would ever recover and progress would be without detah and hayley in leadership roles.. I have actually SEEN both of these people treat myself and others either in officerchat or in private with such disrespect and downright cheating methods (such as having others bid on an item so that others couldnt get, I saw personally one incident, and have heard rumors of 2 others from people that I would trust more than either hayley or detah), and most of you would have left a long time ago.. I didnt say anything about them, so for that I am just as guilty, and punishment for me for that is to not be in the guild... <br>
<br>
detah really likes to say that I &quot;act all high and mighty&quot;, and you know what, I like that, thanks Detah!! I dont cheat people out of anything, I at least try to treat people <br>
with basic respect (until they show me disrespect first, detah), and I like to give the benefit of the doubt, until they show that they arent worthy of that.. I also dont show <br>
two faces.. I dont say how glad I am to see someone playing again, only to call them a &quot;little bitch&quot; and &quot;dont have much respect for a woman who would throw away her children <br>
^_^&quot;.. thats right folks, detah, was so happy to see jorran come back to playing the game just a few weeks ago, sends those as tells after she deguilded.. no asking why, just went <br>
straight to the attitude that Ive seen far too many times.. <br>
mvancexedia: so, even if my intentions were to deguild as an officer to become a regular member were dashed right then and there... <br>
<br>
while Im thinking about it, I have 12kpp worth of cash, and 2 backpacks worth of junk loot/pearls/dots that belong to the guild, and a couple mules with spells looted on raids, and shissarbane weapons that belong to the guild as well.. I'll be needing to get those to someone still in the guild.. <br>
In the end, everybody has to do what they feel is right, and this is what I feel is right for myself.. I got in this guild because of a technicallity, tried my best to help the <br>
guild grow (despite detah's claim that I have done one thing to help this guild).. I didnt ask to be an officer, they came to me.. the only raid I ever asked that we do for selfish reasons was CT Ring of Slime, and the one time the one item I wanted from there dropped, I did not bid so that others could get, even though I wanted them badly.. and even then I was called names in officer channel.. I hate raiding with a passion, but yet I leave the guild with the most dkp of any caster (and coincidentally didnt do the burn dkp and leave thing).. yes my friends, I am a selfish bastard and everything that the people that dont like me will say about me is true.. <br>
<br>
I hope you all the best of luck, and enjoy what you are doing when you are playing this game.. feel free to send tells to jorran and myself, because Im sure we'll be looking for <br>
more for xp a lot since we wont be raiding much.. now, more than ever, the sig at the bottom speaks the truth... <br>
<br>
